#use kore url er moddhei website er id likhe furut kore website er ek pash theke arek pashe jabar golpo jenechi

#youtube videos jekono jayga theke start korar way shikhechi

https://www.howtogeek.com/356563/what-is-a-url-uniform-resource-locator/



Bepar gulo chenar por kaj hocche jekono ekta website a jawa.
Okhaner console a jawa
type koro je window.location
tahole orai sob detailed information janiye dibe konta protocol,konta host,hostname,pathname etc.


site ta abar reload korar jonno location.reaload()
location change kore deyar khetre ek site er href copy kore ene bole deya jay console er moddhe:
location.href=""
tahole ar alada kore oi upore url change kore copy kora link boshate hobe na
Chaile eta ke location.assin("") kora jay